\begin{talent}[T-1]{Wizard Sight}
d106 6
a111 6
of the spell or until the entity is wakened by another entity (by
being shaken, etc.). The target may not be wakened if the spell is
Rank 10 or higher, but must continue to sleep until the spell wears
off.  If a General Knowledge counterspell of this college is cast
upon an affected target by any Adept then the spell will immediate
dissipate and the target can then be woken normally.
