This spell allows the Adept to project a sticky web from their
fingertips.

The caster projects a web, similar to a spider web in construction,
from their fingertips at a target hex, object or entity. Any objects
or entities standing between the caster and the target are ensnared by
the web along with the target. The web may only ensnare a number of
human-sized entities equal to the caster's rank and so will stop at
the hex at which this limit is reached (or maximum range).
