\subsection{Base Chance Modefiers}
d19 3
a21 3
spell, or ritual of the College except as listed in
\ref{magic:modefiers} or under the descriptions of the specific
spells, talents, and rituals of the College.
d28 2
a29 2
{\em Experience Multiple:} 150 \\
{\em Base Chance:} Perception + 4\% / Rank \\
d34 2
a35 1
invisible by magical means (i.e. Walking Unseen, Blending, Invisibility).
d42 14
a55 21
{\em Range:}  15 feet + 15 / Rank \\
{\em Duration:} 1 hour + 1/ Rank \\
{\em Experience Multiple:} 250 \\
{\em Base Chance:} 15\% \\
{\em Resist:} May actively \& passively resisted \\
{\em Storage:} Investment, Ward \\
{\em Target:} Entity \\
\end{spelldesc}
{\em Effects:} The effects of this spell are identical to those for
the spell of that name (S-1) of the College of Naming Incantations (\S
\ref{namer:charm}) except that the target's Generic True Name need not
be known to cast the spell.  If the Generic True Name is known, the
Base Chance is increased by 15\%.  If the Individual True Name is
known and used, the Base Chance is increased by 25\%.

\textbf{Description from Namer:} {\emph
The Namer may influence theactions of any one entity
whose Generic Name he knows by casting a Spell of Charming over the
individual.  If, in addition, the Namer knows and pronounces the
victim's Individual True Name, the Base Chance of the spell taking
effect is increased by 50 and the effect of the spell is increased.
d57 1
a57 1
and will readily accept most suggestions emanating from him.  Sworn
d63 1
a63 1
to act in a certain way on pain of losing the caster's ``friendship''.
d67 1
a67 1
upon 90\% of the time.  The caster may only ensure 100\% compliance
d69 9
a77 7
binds the victim and caster together.  In such instances, however, the
victim immediately makes a Resistance Check.  If he resists, then the
spell is broken.  Otherwise, the victim will accept the order and be
100\% faithful to it for the remainder of the spell.  Whenever any
suggestion is made that would lead to the victim's injury or death,
another Resistance Check is made.  If the check is unsuccessful, the
victim will accept the suggestion, otherwise the spell will be broken.}
d82 12
a93 11
{\em Range:}  15 feet + 15 / Rank \\
{\em Duration:} 10 seconds + 10 / Rank \\
{\em Experience Multiple:} 300 \\
