{\em Effects:}  Allows the Adept to lift 2 pounds and move it at the
rate of one mile an hour.  The Adept may move an additional 5 pounds or
move the chosen target at an additional 2 miles an hour per Rank.
d98 14
a111 14
{\em Range:}  15 feet + 15 / Rank \\
{\em Duration:} 1 hour + 1 / Rank \\
{\em Experience Multiple:} 250 \\
{\em Base Chance:} 15\% \\
{\em Resist:} May be actively \& passively resisted \\
{\em Storage:} Investment, Ward, Magical Trap \\
{\em Target:} Entity \\
\end{spelldesc}
{\em Effects:} The Adept may send 1 entity which, normally spends any
time sleeping into a deep enchanted sleep which will last for the
duration of the spell or until the entity is wakened by another entity
(by being shaken, etc.).  The target may not be wakened if the spell
is Rank 10 or higher, but must continue to sleep until the spell wears
off.
d116 21
a136 21
{\em Range:} 15 feet + 15 / Rank \\
{\em Duration:}	1 hour + 1 / Rank \\
{\em Experience Multiple:} 100 \\
{\em Base Chance:} 40\% \\
{\em Resist:} May not be resisted \\
{\em Storage:} Investment, Potion, Ward \\
{\em Target:} Entity \\
\end{spelldesc}
{\em Effects:} The target of this spell may move unnoticed, not
invisible.  If the target of the spell, or the target's possessions,
are touched by another entity, or that entity's possessions, then the
spell is broken.  An entity's possessions are those non-entity things
which the entity is wearing or carrying at that time.  An unconscious
or sleeping entity is not a possession, it is still an entity. The
target of the spell may not break it voluntarily (other than by, for
example, touching another entity). Once broken the spell most be
recast.

