d429 34
a462 21
{\em Range:}  15 feet + 15 / Rank \\
{\em Duration:} Concentration: Maximum 15 minutes + 15 / Rank \\
{\em Experience Multiple:} 150 \\
{\em Base Chance:} 35\% \\
{\em Resist:} May only be passively resisted \\
{\em Storage:} Investment, Ward \\
{\em Target:} Entity or object \\
\end{spelldesc}
{\em Effects: }This spell wiorks similarly to the Web of Fire Spell
(S-4) in the College of Fire Magics except that it allows the Adept to
project a sticky web instead of a web of fire from their fingertips.
Any objects or individuals immediately between the caster and the
target of the spell (along the flight path of the web) will be struck
by the web and ensnared.  The web can ensnare a number of human-sized
targets equal to the Rank of the spell.  Ensnared characters may not
move, and can only take actions in every other pulse.  In order to
free themself from the web, each ensnared character must roll under or
equal to Physical Strength or cut successfully cut the web.  The web
is cut whenever any Strike against it with a weapon that is rated for
type B damage results in 10 or more Damage Points to the web.  Once
any character cuts the web, all characters cease to be ensnared by it.
